701115f-a.title: Bronx: Givan Avenue - Corosa Avenue
701115f-a.text:
Givan Ave. (from left fore to background), east from but not includ-
ing Corsa Ave., as it crosses Eastchester Road.
November 11, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.

700803f-a.title: Bronx: Corsa Avenue - Givan Avenue
700803f-a.text:
Corsa Ave., north from Givan Ave., to and including Boston Road.
On the left appear the rears of houses facing on the east side of Fenton
Ave., and in the background is visible Public School No. 78 on the
north side of Hicks Street.
November 11, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
